      "content": "i just don't get why you keep using the \"fundamental right\" argument like it's a settled fact. isnt that just a political opinion to justify more government spending? shouldn't a neutral analyst acknowledge that for many people, individual liberty and free market choice are more important than state-mandated coverage?",
